Detailed Description

CBTDiscoverer class is responsible for scanning a remote device for bluetooth serial port services.

Following are some main functions of this class:

  1. Scan serial port services on a bluetooth device.
  2. Construct a UI to display them to the user for selection.

void CBTDiscoverer::AttributeRequestComplete (  TSdpServRecordHandle  aHandle,
TInt  aError
)  [private]
 

Callback method from system.

This method is a call back from system and is invoked when the attribute list of a service ends. When this method is invoked it is guaranteed the port number and the port name of the serial port service on the device is available. This number and name is then written to the list contained by CBTServiceListContainer.

Parameters:
aHandle as TSdpServRecordHandle type. Represents the Handle to the service record.
aError as TInt. Represents an error code.

void CBTDiscoverer::AttributeRequestResult (  TSdpServRecordHandle  aHandle,
TSdpAttributeID  aAttrID,
CSdpAttrValue *  aAttrValue
)  [private]
 

Callback method from system.

This method is a call back from system and is invoked when the Bluetooth service discovery agent finds an attribute for a particular service requested by NextRecordRequestComplete() method. This method then further requests to visit the value of the received attribute.

Parameters:
aHandle as TSdpServRecordHandle type. Represents the Handle to the service record.
aAttrID as TSdpAttributeID. Represents the attribute id.
aAttrValue as CSdpAttrValue object pointer. Represents attribute value.

void CBTDiscoverer::NextRecordRequestComplete (  TInt  aError,
TSdpServRecordHandle  aHandle,
TInt  aTotalRecordsCount
)  [private]
 

Callback method from system.

This method is a call back from system and is invoked when the Bluetooth service discovery agent finds a service matching the service criteria specified in ConstructL(). This method then further requests attributes for the discovered service.

Parameters:
aError as TInt. Represents an error code.
aHandle as TSdpServRecordHandle type. Represents the Handle to the service record.
aTotalRecordsCount as TInt. 0 if no record is found.
